<div style="font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #0f172a; max-width: 560px;">
  <h2 style="margin-bottom: 8px; color: #1e3a8a;">Welcome to PayrollPilot</h2>
  <p>Hi {{fullName}},</p>
  <p>Your employee profile has been created by HR. Here are your details:</p>
  <ul style="padding-left: 18px;">
    <li><strong>Employee code:</strong> {{employeeCode}}</li>
    <li><strong>Job title:</strong> {{jobTitle}}</li>
    <li><strong>Department:</strong> {{department}}</li>
    <li><strong>Work email:</strong> {{email}}</li>
  </ul>
  <p style="margin: 20px 0;">
    <a
      href="{{setupPasswordUrl}}"
      style="display: inline-block; background: #2563eb; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; padding: 12px 20px; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600;"
    >
      Set up your password
    </a>
  </p>
  <p style="font-size: 13px; color: #475569;">
    After setting your password, sign in to view your profile and download salary slips.
  </p>
  <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #64748b; word-break: break-all;">
    If the button does not work, copy this link:<br />
    {{setupPasswordUrl}}
  </p>
  <p style="margin-top: 16px;">Regards,<br />PayrollPilot Team</p>
</div>
